results.description: The English Football League begins a formal investigation into Macclesfield Town's failure to pay their players.
results.title: Macclesfield Town: EFL investigating non-payment of wages

results.description: Macclesfield Town players are advised not to play or train because they are not currently insured.
results.shortTitle: Macclesfield advised not to play or train
results.title: Macclesfield Town: 'Uninsured' striking players advised not to play or train

results.description: Strike-hit Macclesfield Town are content to avoid "a cricket score" after an FA Cup first-round upset at the hands of seventh-tier side Kingstonian.
results.title: Macclesfield Town 0-4 Kingstonian: Strike-hit club happy to avoid 'cricket score' defeat

thumbnail.altText: Kingstonian celebrate victory over Macclesfield Town

results.description: Watch highlights as crisis-hit Macclesfield Town suffer an FA Cup first-round upset at the hands of seventh-tier side Kingstonian.
results.title: FA Cup: Macclesfield Town 0-4 Kingstonian highlights

results.description: Macclesfield say their FA Cup tie against Kingstonian will go ahead despite the club's players going on strike over unpaid wages.
results.shortTitle: Macc FA Cup tie to go ahead despite strike
results.title: FA Cup: Macclesfield v Kingstonian to go ahead despite Silkmen player strike

results.description: Relive all the action from Sunday's 10 FA Cup first-round ties, including Maldon & Tiptree stunning Leyton Orient.
results.title: FA Cup: Sunday's first-round action as it happened

results.description: Listen to local radio commentaries from nine FA Cup first-round ties.
results.shortTitle: Listen: Hayes & Yeading v Oxford United
results.title: Listen: FA Cup first round commentaries including Bristol Rovers & Leyton Orient

results.description: Joe Sealey, the son of former Manchester United goalkeeper Les, says he wants to buy Macclesfield Town and can help sustain the club.
results.shortTitle: Sealey wants to buy Macclesfield Town
results.title: Macclesfield Town: Local businessman Joe Sealey wants to buy League Two club

results.description: Macclesfield players strike over unpaid wages, putting their place in the the FA Cup both this season and in 2020-21 at risk.
results.shortTitle: Macc cup place at risk as players strike
results.title: FA Cup: Macclesfield Town's place at risk as players strike over unpaid wages

results.description: Macclesfield Town players could strike over unpaid wages and cost the club its place in the FA Cup both this season and in 2020-21.
results.shortTitle: Cup place risk if Silkmen players strike
results.title: FA Cup: Macclesfield Town place at risk as League Two club's players threaten to strike over unpaid wages

results.description: Ryan Loft's late winner gives struggling Carlisle an important victory as they come from behind to beat Macclesfield Town.
results.title: Carlisle United 2-1 Macclesfield Town

results.description: Macclesfield players and staff are told by the club they will not be paid on time, BBC Radio Manchester reports.
results.shortTitle: Silkmen players will not be paid on time
results.title: Macclesfield Town: Players and staff told they will not be paid October wages on time

results.description: Saturday's League Two game between Macclesfield Town and Bradford City is postponed because of a waterlogged pitch.
results.title: Macclesfield Town P-P Bradford City

results.description: A winding-up petition issued against Macclesfield Town is adjourned, as the club's lawyer says Brexit is having an impact.
results.title: Macclesfield Town: Brexit having "impact" on club as winding-up petition adjourned

results.description: Cheltenham cruise to a 3-0 home win over Macclesfield to maintain their fine run in League Two.
results.title: Cheltenham Town 3-0 Macclesfield Town

results.description: Jak McCourt's superb late goal hands Macclesfield a dramatic victory at struggling Oldham.
results.title: Oldham Athletic 0-1 Macclesfield Town

results.description: Paddy Osadebe hits the winner as Macclesfield come from behind to beat Port Vale 2-1 at Moss Rose.
results.title: Macclesfield Town 2-1 Port Vale

results.description: Sam Smith scores a late equaliser for Cambridge who share the points with Macclesfield in a 2-2 draw.
results.title: Cambridge United 2-2 Macclesfield Town

results.description: Macclesfield Town players and staff ask the English Football League for help as their wages are once again not paid.
results.shortTitle: Silkmen ask EFL for help on unpaid wages
results.title: Macclesfield Town players and staff ask EFL for help after wages go unpaid

results.description: Theo Robinson hits a first-half equaliser for Colchester as Macclesfield are held to a 1-1 draw at Moss Rose.
results.title: Macclesfield Town 1-1 Colchester United
